Amendment to the PENSION BENEFITS STANDARDS REGULATIONS, 1985 concerning
the implementation of the prudent person approach to the investments of
pension plans and following a five-step approach to the investment rules:
(i) Quantitative Limits (ii) Level of Prudence (iii) Investment Policy
(iv) Self-dealing Rules (v) Filing Requirements
